# Styling Conventions

## Colors — `AppColors`

Always use `AppColors` constants. Never use raw `Color(0x...)` inline.

```dart
// ✅ GOOD
color: AppColors.primaryColor

// ❌ BAD
color: Color(0xFF023E8A)
```

| Constant | Hex | Use |
|---|---|---|
| `primaryColor` | `#023E8A` | Primary actions, active states |
| `lightPrimaryColor` | `#023E8A` | Same as primary (alias) |
| `secondaryColor` | `#E6F1FF` | Backgrounds, chips, badges |
| `lightsecondaryColor` | `#FFFFFF` | White surfaces |

## Typography — `TextStyles`

All text styles are in `lib/core/utils/app_text_styles.dart`. Always call them with `BuildContext`.

```dart
// ✅ GOOD
Text('Hello', style: TextStyles.semiBold16(context))

// ❌ BAD
Text('Hello', style: TextStyle(fontSize: 16, fontWeight: FontWeight.w600))
```

Available styles (format: `{weight}{size}`):

- `regular11`, `semiBold11`
- `regular12`, `regular13`, `bold13`, `semiBold13`
- `regular14`, `medium14`, `semiBold14`
- `medium15`, `semiBold15`
- `regular16`, `medium16`, `semiBold16`, `bold16`
- `regular18`, `medium18`, `bold18`
- `semiBold19`, `bold19`
- `regular20`, `medium20`, `semiBold20`
- `regular22`, `bold22`, `bold23`
- `semiBold24`, `regular26`, `bold28`

To tint: `.copyWith(color: AppColors.primaryColor)`.

## Sizing — `flutter_screenutil`

Design size is **375×812**. Always use `.w`, `.h`, `.r`, `.sp` — never raw doubles for layout.

```dart
// ✅ GOOD
SizedBox(width: 24.w, height: 8.h)
BorderRadius.circular(12.r)

// ❌ BAD
SizedBox(width: 24, height: 8)
```

## Fonts

| Locale | Font Family |
|--------|-------------|
| `ar` | `Cairo` (400/500/600/700) |
| `en` | `Inter` (400/500/600/700) |

The font family is set globally in `MaterialApp` based on locale. Never override `fontFamily` in individual `TextStyle`.

## Assets

Images are in `assets/images/` and `assets/images/vuesax/bold|outline/`. Reference via the generated `AppImages` class in `lib/core/utils/app_images.dart`.

SVGs use `flutter_svg`; rasters use standard `Image.asset`.
